{
  "name": "DataSource",
  "summary": "",
  "description": "<p>代表容器应用程序的一个数据源对象。</p>",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Type",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回DataSource的类型。只读。</p>",
      "examples": "",
      "parameters": [],
      "type": "Number",
      "value": "",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Activate",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p></p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(29, 31, 32); --darkreader-inline-bgcolor:#17191a;\" data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor=\"\">激活数据源，跨进程表现为激活ET文档。</span>",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code class=\"JavaScript\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//以下示例为WPP激活数据源对象，调起ET文档</span>\nApplication<span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.ActivePresentation</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.Slides</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)<span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.Shapes</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)<span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.WebShape</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.DataSource</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.Activate</span>()</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "Boolean"
    },
    {
      "name": "ApplyDemoRange",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>往活动单元格填充示例数据。返回DataRange。</p><p></p>",
      "examples": "",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "Object"
    },
    {
      "name": "CreateDataRange",
      "summary": "<p>参数Range可以为代表单元格的字符串或者Range对象，当为空或字符串时，会弹出对话框输入单元格地址。形如“sheet1!$a$1”的字符串表示sheet1中A1单元格。返回值为DataRange。</p>",
      "description": "<p>为选定的单元格创建DataRange对象。</p>",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code class=\"JavaScript\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//下列示例为Sheet1中的A1单元格创建DataRange对象</span>\nApplication.ActiveWorkbook.Sheets.Item(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).Shapes.Item(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).WebShape.DataSource.CreateDataRange(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"sheet1!<span class=\"hljs-subst\">$a</span><span class=\"hljs-subst\">$1</span>\"</span>)</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Range",
          "type": "Variant",
          "description": "代表单元格的字符串或者Range对象。",
          "default": "",
          "optional": true,
          "nullable": ""
        }
      ],
      "returns": "Object"
    },
    {
      "name": "GetAllRangeInfo",
      "summary": "<p>返回的字符串以JSON模式记录所有DataRange的Key。</p>",
      "description": "<p></p><p>获取所有已注册的DataRange。</p>",
      "examples": "",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "String"
    },
    {
      "name": "GetDataRange",
      "summary": "<p>目前Index仅支持字符串，代表DataRange对象的键。当输入的Index为数字时，不会有类型检查报错，但是也不会有对象返回。</p>",
      "description": "<p>返回已注册的对应DataRange。</p>",
      "examples": "",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
